          %p A Design Plan is given to the client with suggestions of specific colors, fabrics, materials, furniture and accessories necessary to complete the look. Complete with a Design Board, client will have all the shopping information and swatches necessary to implement the plan completely. 
          %p Client is given an estimate of how much time it will take to complete the project and receive a weekly update to know the status of the project, number of hours of services rendered and budget analysis.
      .content-type-1#page3-sub3-page
