          %p e-Decorating is a perfect design option that gives virtual clients the opportunity to retain the services of Bridget Chirigos, even if they live outside of Houston or prefer a more affordable way to design their space. With e-Decorating you can achieve the look you want within your time, distance or budget.
          %p All you do is fill out a design questionnaire and send it back along with photos and measurements of your space to be designed and we will provide you with all necessary information to implement the design.  For more details and to get started, go to our e-Decorating page. 
